text: Whitehorse is the capital of Yukon, Canada. It is also the largest city in northern Canada. It is on the Alaska Highway and the Yukon River. ==History== The city was inhabited by First Nations for thousands of years. == References == == Related pages == * Dawson City, Yukon Category:Cities in Canada Category:Provincial and territorial capitals of Canada Category:Settlements in Yukon
title: Whitehorse
